Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.14,0:22:21.88,JPED,,0,0,0,,but can feel my butterfly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.04,0:22:25.62,JPED,,0,0,0,,試行錯誤の勝率は(in the future)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.62,0:22:28.64,JPED,,0,0,0,,後で言い出そう(so take it easy)
