Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.82,0:22:38.82,JPED,,0,0,0,,難解なrelationも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.98,0:22:40.76,JPED,,0,0,0,,熱くなれない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.76,0:22:43.48,JPED,,0,0,0,,心を放て
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.66,0:22:47.20,JPED,,0,0,0,,make us freeなsplash 重ねた
