Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:45.28,ZWED,,0,0,0,,水花四溅 我们在此获得自由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.50,0:21:49.20,ZWED,,0,0,0,,沐浴在光的对照中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:52.76,ZWED,,0,0,0,,跃入水中 我们今天获得自由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.50,0:22:00.52,ZWED,,0,0,0,,随心所欲地 say say say
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.26,0:22:04.30,ZWED,,0,0,0,,用自己的方式 kick kick kick
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.94,0:22:08.04,ZWED,,0,0,0,,想紧紧抓住 pull pull pull
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.66,0:22:17.86,ZWED,,0,0,0,,是否没有日落之时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.14,0:22:21.88,ZWED,,0,0,0,,but can feel my butterfly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.04,0:22:25.62,ZWED,,0,0,0,,从失败中寻找成功的胜率是多少（in the future）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.62,0:22:28.64,ZWED,,0,0,0,,以后再告诉你吧(so take it easy)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.38,0:22:32.90,ZWED,,0,0,0,,浸湿吧(划过水的手指)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.90,0:22:36.70,ZWED,,0,0,0,,涌入的感情(满足渴求吧)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.82,0:22:38.82,ZWED,,0,0,0,,对复杂的relation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.98,0:22:40.76,ZWED,,0,0,0,,完全提不起劲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.76,0:22:43.48,ZWED,,0,0,0,,就敞开心扉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.66,0:22:47.20,ZWED,,0,0,0,,水花四溅 我们在此获得自由
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.44,0:22:51.06,ZWED,,0,0,0,,在光的对照中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.14,0:22:58.18,ZWED,,0,0,0,,凝视那永不完结的夏季
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.40,0:23:02.46,ZWED,,0,0,0,,各随己愿 say say say
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.12,0:23:06.02,ZWED,,0,0,0,,伸出手来 deep deep deep
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.02,0:23:07.22,ZWED,,0,0,0,,splash free
